   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="inscription" xml:lang="en" decls="#f_S #c_1 #m_IF #t_P">
            <ab>IN MEMORY OF</ab>
            <ab>JANET SPOTTISWOODE WEIR</ab>
            <ab>---------------</ab>
            <ab>BORN IN EDINBURGH</ab>
            <ab>22ND JANUARY,1824.</ab>
            <ab>DIED IN ROME</ab>
            <ab>17TH FEBRUARY, 1883.</ab>
            <ab>----------------</ab>
            <ab rend="Alignl">"WHERE IS MY GRAVE? NEATH SOME FOREIGN SKY</ab>
            <ab rend="Alignl">SHALL I LAY DOWN MY WEARIED LIMBS AND DIE?</ab>
            <ab rend="Alignl">. . . . . . . . . . . . .</ab>
            <ab rend="Alignl">WHERE IS MY GRAVE? IT MATTERS NOT WHERE!</ab>
            <ab rend="Alignl">BUT MY HOME BEYOND - IT IS THERE, IT IS THERE</ab>
            <ab rend="Alignl">WHERE GOD WIPES TEARS FROM EVERY EYE</ab>
            <ab rend="Alignl">AND THE LAMB IS THE LIGHT OF A SUNLESS SKY".</ab>
            <ab rend="Alignr">MONSELL</ab>
         </div>
      </body>
